    "date": "2026-05-29T14:19:59Z",
    "text": "Benton MacKaye National Scenic Trail Feasibility Study Act of 2026\n\nThis bill requires the Department of Agriculture to study the feasibility of designating the Benton\u00a0MacKaye Trail (located in Georgia, Tennessee, and North Carolina) as a national scenic trail."
